Juliet Cowan https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Juliet_Cowan 0 Juliet Cowan (born 21 May 1974 in Belfast, Northern Ireland) is a British television, film and stage actress. Cowan has had various TV guest star roles in long-running shows such as EastEnders, Silent Witness and Casualty. Cowan has also had a recurring role in CBBC show The Sarah Jane Adventures and This Life.
